1. To create folder:
  - mkdir Name => this will create a folder with name 'Name'
  - mkdir Name\Sub => this will create 'Name' then inside it 'Sub'
  - mkdir n\1 n\2 n\3 => this will create multiple folders

2. To create file:
  - type null > file.txt => this will create a file 'file.txt'
  - type null > app\file.txt => create 'file.txt' inside folder app

3. To Save all installed Dependencies:
  - pip freeze > requirements.txt

4. Create & Run virtual env:
  - python -m venv Name => create virtual environment
  - Name\Scripts\activate => activate virtual environment
  - deactivate => to deactivate

5. Run the Backend:
  - uvicorn app.main:app --reload => here 'app.main' is the entry point

6. Push to github: 1️⃣ Stage your changes
  - git add .
  2️⃣ Commit your changes
  - git commit -m "your commit message"
  3️⃣ Push to the remote repository
  - git push origin main

7. To pull from github:
  - git pull origin main
